{"tid":1671312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【我宣佈星期五返工前遊行焦點】四警察協會質問段校長識唔識法治，實在太囂張","createTime":"2019-10-23T11:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T15:33:35.000Z","uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"07a0750b0eb8660fb3008e0c44ebee2bbe7ba71a","tid":1671312,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:42:59.000Z","msg":"睇路唔係換特首喇～換邊個都係盧偉聰治港，係咪？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【香港電台】四警協會發信段崇智：校長明白何謂法治嗎？<br />\n四個警察員方協會向中大校長段崇智發公開信，指段崇智早前發出的公開信偏頗，反映他在培育學生及管理教育機構方面的能力，遠遜於其學術成就。公開信指，段崇智對學生所述的經歷不抱任何懷疑，又對學生被捕前，涉嫌干犯嚴重罪行隻字不提。公開信批評段崇智在沒事實基礎、忽視求證下，單憑被捕學生的片面之詞，便公開質疑警方，四個協會表示極度遺憾，又批評段崇智明知有學生已經干犯罪行仍加以包庇，是自毀大學公信力的舉動。<br />\n<br />\n協會又引述段崇智的公開信，曾提及要於現有機制以外，嚴正跟進警員涉嫌違規，協會反問「段校長明白何謂法治嗎」，指難以理解為何被捕中大學生，可獲有別於其他香港市民的對待，反問中大學生是否有特權。協會指形容建議荒誕，難以相信會由大學校長提出。<br />\n<br />\n協會又指段崇智公開支持學生是開了很壞的先例，認為會令其他被捕學生向其他大學校長施壓，以達成他們「洗白」暴動罪行的目的。協會指段崇智明確將政治衝突帶入校園，誓必將整個教育界推向萬劫不復的境地。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #段崇智 #警司協會 #香港警務督察協會 #海外督察協會 #警察隊員佐級協會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/posts/2908846719223365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fposts%2F2908846719223365&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=63ca2323\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/posts/2908846719223365</a>"},{"pid":"cd4dcccd3ad4fc5497221d0bea2862d31f4ff0da","tid":1671312,"uid":310850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/boycottextraditionlaw/photos/a.977877379225626/1058149987865031/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fboycottextraditionlaw%2Fphotos%2Fa.977877379225626%2F1058149987865031%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=82fdc144\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/boycottextraditionlaw/photos/a.977877379225626/1058149987865031/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjrRZwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjrRZwt.jpg&h=c035ba9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"095334c49e795aefae05463ff4ede094e89130d4","tid":1671312,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLCRe5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLCRe5c.png&h=dab3e99d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ph7ecRT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fph7ecRT.png&h=6096c8fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2d33e1917f82f5baf66beaa33ce1a0ee23eacee","tid":1671312,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"未審先判又叫法治？"},{"pid":"d1190e96d5d86fff57e57187ec20992d7201ec04","tid":1671312,"uid":31151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:50:46.000Z","msg":"4個協會由上至下有邊個學歷高過段崇智?教人咩叫法治?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ab13f7d10e6e1f115d1b980956547feecb0dd5","tid":1671312,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:51:52.000Z","msg":"咁嘅時勢，好認同上星期六愛丁堡廣場嘅集會大嗌「SOS」，呼籲海外派救護員同觀察員來香港睇住呢個警察城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際文宣手足真係要全力谷～唔係唔係段校長可以撐到幾耐～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【國際人道救援祈禱會】現場直播<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/508924519670204/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F508924519670204%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=8572296b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/508924519670204/</a>"},{"pid":"a1ca1500685be8a097ce28c8311a0787431c8e72","tid":1671312,"uid":57490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:51:57.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 呢班垃圾真係冇撚得救"},{"pid":"928f82feff964cd18e9ab115248c37d2a35d860c","tid":1671312,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"垃圾康樂會，出咩聲明"},{"pid":"669dd9b266fe17280a9ed24772875c42afbd2095","tid":1671312,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e68c13847a0e3f215fd738800862c10ec526e641","tid":1671312,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"以後警察唔好去暴大進修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6a22708ae89a43309da90a930dbe4e7e7d288b","tid":1671312,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:00:06.000Z","msg":"咁早起唔到身嘅手足，都要用金魔法「懲罰」下中大，支持段校長：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>#CU9550<br />\n&quot;Re: #CU9545<br />\n一齊保護段校長<br />\n<br />\n有眾多消息指段校長有可能被逼辭，藍絲校友拉隊退捐。中大好有可能跟隨國泰成為下一個迫跪嘅機構。<br />\n<br />\n既然段校長行咗第一步，我哋學生/家長/校友/教職員/市民/社會賢達都要行前一步保護返校長。<br />\n<br />\n大家最容易做嘅就係課金，抗衡下藍絲退捐條線。<br />\n<br />\n保護段校長課金攻略<br />\n1. 前往 <a href=\"https://cloud.itsc.cuhk.edu.hk/forms/forms/18.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloud.itsc.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fforms%2Fforms%2F18.aspx&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=1b689722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cloud.itsc.cuhk.edu.hk/forms/forms/18.aspx</a><br />\n2. 捐贈意願 Donation Purpose 揀 「其他 (Others)」<br />\n3. 註 Remarks 寫「本人的捐款是為了支持段校長公開信中支援被捕學生及保衛校園的相關項目」<br />\n4. 暫時建議單次捐款，再補多個定期捐款<br />\n5. 就自己接受程度填寫個人可披露資料，當然越實名越好<br />\n6. 捐款後會見到：<a href=\"https://imgur.com/dvZwtue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FdvZwtue&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=c4e33fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/dvZwtue</a><br />\n7. 立即開心share 同tag 朋友，最好加吓啲 #ProtectCUHKChallenge #ProtectVCTuan<br />\n8. 有興趣去埋呢張google form 度講你捐咗幾多集氣（全匿名） <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2oNKRsg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oNKRsg&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=54b735bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2oNKRsg</a><br />\n<br />\n段校長，各位，我哋要齊上齊落。&quot;</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c67d42204d8037cde37ff49fb20c87ffa7257565","tid":1671312,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"推！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202ed8a4588ec5109a24ae2264ff2d88b7fd006e","tid":1671312,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"[國際行動POST] 11月2日 求援國際 堅守自治 維園大集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671252</a>"},{"pid":"833f1770fdcc3ea461a298937f2b0cb3463040f3","tid":1671312,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T1